{"tid":1395934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［下載隨時用］用法律叫停無理攻擊義士行為","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T04:13:57.000Z","uid":239765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b05afae01608815dca5931d9ace4bf118c953b2c","tid":1395934,"uid":239765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgQO9bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgQO9bd.png&h=813d976a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自行簡陋地製作了一張文宣<br />\n用了藍色 想佢地send時以為係自己人整<br />\n希望可叫停一啲怕事藍絲的無理攻擊義士行為<br />\n大家可下載此圖<br />\n舉報或回覆藍絲時 不妨attach<br />\n希望可以憑法律阻嚇劣質行為<br />\n香港人 加油<br />\n<br />\nAdditional info:<br />\n普通法的「破壞或妨礙司法公正罪」（perverting or obstructing the course of justice）是指被告的行為傾向於阻礙，打擊或阻止司法公正。以下例子等同妨礙司法公正罪的行為︰報假案；在宣誓下作假證供（perjury）；妨礙警務人員執行職務；協助匪徒逃避拘捕；<span style=\"color: red;\">干擾證人；干擾或破壞證據；干擾陪審員；發表足以影響公平審訊的言論等。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4d4dc902faf58481a5b0a05d865d7a75fd231fdd","tid":1395934,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56e3e9e733f5970a83f75851abfd0569bb97aa9","tid":1395934,"uid":239765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"29c4c78aa8fbb767f118c0bb51e58aafad7de6d0","tid":1395934,"uid":239765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"push"}]}